title: KEVIN KAY - I WORSHIP GOD
seo_description:
Worship doesn't bless God , it blesses us. Worship moves God to down pour his blessings on you . Worship is the best form of prayer and the only prayer that confuses the devil. Worship is an act of faith.

This song is a blessing to many . Do not only listen to the song, open up your spirit and let the song minister to you. Pray along with the song and watch the manifestation there after. God Bless you .
